Package assn3

Class Recipe

java.lang.Object
assn3.Recipe
public class Recipe extends Object
A Recipe represents a bread recipe with its ingredients and quantity ordered. This is a plain Java class that mainly stores data with getters and setters. Each recipe contains ingredients measurements and tracks how many loaves are ordered.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Yimi Ding
